# Intentionally empty.
# pnpm 11 ignores env-var auth tokens placed in a committed project .npmrc,
# so the npmjs publish token lives in user-level ~/.npmrc instead:
#   npm config set //registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken "npm_<token>"
# The token MUST be a classic *Automation* token (npmjs → Access Tokens →
# Classic Token → Automation). It bypasses 2FA; a "Publish" token does not
# and publishing fails with `E403 … bypass 2fa … required`.
# See RELEASING.md for the full flow.
